{"word":"ἀμνήμων","slug":"ἀμνήμων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμνήμων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μνήμη'><el>μνήμη</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>unmindful, forgetful</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <el>τινός</el> <i>of</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>forgotten, not mentioned</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}